                      <font face="Verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> Friends, Necro's, countrymen.... Lend me your Jonobtiks.<br />Now is the winter of our incontinence... ah crap, nevermind.<br /><br />Basically, the fact that our pets require a fecking peridot as well as bone chips to summon is wearing a little thin... We must unite!<br /><br />Why do our pets cost so much in comparison to other pet classes? They're not really any better <img src="images/banghead_125.gif" border="0" alt="" title="" align="middle" /><br /><br />Clerics can cast group Aego, or even AE Aego, for the price of one summon of our pets.<br /><br />I didn't mind too much before, but with the coming of PoP, and the necessity of soloing 400+ hitting mobs, I go through pets fast. coupled with the fact that some people on dial up connections have to reconnect every 2 hours or so. This runs up quite a bill in reagents.<br /><br />Needless to say, our time has come! We must use the almighty /feedback to get rid of this outdated tradition. Yes, /feedback does work if used in bulk.... remember our original spell line up for PoP? Every necro /feedbacked what total shit it was, and they twinked those spells into the hardcore line up we have today.<br /><br />Either way, it's worth a try - Having to buy peridots is a pain in the arse. Every freedom loving necro... /feedback today! Rid Norrath of this ghey reagent!<img src="images/jump_125.gif" border="0" alt="" title="" align="middle" /><br /><br />Lich Deyac Saah<br />Antonius Bayle<br /><br /><br /></span id="msg"></font>
